Review.Titre: Ordered 4 of the same gas valves for an…
Review.Contenu: Ordered 4 of the same gas valves for an atosa fryer.  2 for a repair and 2 as “stock” in my shop.  All supposed to be “genuine” Atosa parts.  1 was and the other 3 were made who know where.  Installed 2 of them and one was bad.  Good thing I ordered extra.  Tried to get it replaced under warranty to replenish my stock.  Took 3 weeks to get a warranty claim and part.  Valve 2 is installed and not working now.  Only one working is the actual genuine part they sent me.  Trying to return the others but they are ignoring me.  Finally threatened to report them and all of the sudden have a response.  Now we will see how long it takes to get my money back.  BUYER BEWARE.  Operator out of Illinois, registered in TX as a “foreign LLC”, based out of china, and customer service is in India.  You get what you pay for….will never buy from again!!!
